title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception throws when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data export process should proceed without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 

1. Open the attached report. 
2. Find a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 
3. Preview the report. 
4. Attempt to export the data from the table and observe if an exception is thrown.
